						               													<description>The night is still young and the Party community starts off to find the best Party in town. For now the streets are full of people but soon the vibe will rise on the dance floors. Who is the host making the most money out of his guests? Who throws the coolest Party? And which Party will end in a brawl?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Dice Party is a dice game for 2-4 players in which every player acts as a party host, throwing a party that competes with the parties of the other players. Each player has up to 60 dice to throw, representing party guests of three types: cool Party People (yellow), high society VIPs (orange) and experience-driven rowdys, referred to as Mob (red).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;While each round is a tactical challenge, since you have three different win conditions to outreach your opponents, the game unfolds its strategic depth with its Party Animal mode. Playing this full mode you're playing multiple rounds, trying to achieve complete victory by winning once with each of the 3 victory conditions:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     All other Partys escalate due to their Mob guests.&amp;#10;     A VIP millionaire hits your Party.&amp;#10;     You pickpocket six wallets from your Party People.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
